## 📦 Do's & Don'ts

Two cards **side by side** (`display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr`). Do on the left, Don't on the right. On mobile they stack.

```astro
<div class="dos-donts">
  <div class="dos-donts__col dos-donts__col--do">
    <p class="dos-donts__label">Do</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Rule</strong> — short reason.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="dos-donts__col dos-donts__col--dont">
    <p class="dos-donts__label">Don't</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Rule</strong> — short reason.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>
```

CSS for the grid:

```css
.dos-donts {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 16px;
  margin: 16px 0 24px;
}
@media (max-width: 600px) { .dos-donts { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
```

---

## 📦 Related

After `<hr />`, a single `<p>` with bold component names linked to their pages, separated by ` · `:

```astro
<hr />
<p>
  <strong>Related:</strong>
  <a href="/components/button">Button</a> — one-line reason.
  ·
  <a href="/components/option-card">Option Card</a> — one-line reason.
</p>
```

